{"tid":1970152,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"43歲本地婦西環遭非禮 27歲印度夫打傷同鄉色狼","createTime":"2020-04-13T02:43:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-13T02:56:53.000Z","uid":128369,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f199e700d7761c06d9d4e3bc2b5683159fed005a","tid":1970152,"uid":128369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T02:43:22.000Z","msg":"一名43歲本地女子昨晚在西區正街與第三街交界，懷疑被一名23歲印度裔男子非禮，女事主以手提電話襲擊對方作還擊，在附近的女事主27歲印度裔丈夫見狀，亦以手襲擊該名懷疑色狼。<br />\n<br />\n警員昨晚10時44分接報到場，經初步調查，23歲男子涉嫌非禮被捕，事主兩夫婦則涉嫌襲擊致造成實際身體傷害被捕，案件交由西區警區刑事調查隊第四隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n23歲男子肩、頭及手受傷，清醒被送往瑪麗醫院治理。據悉，涉嫌非禮的疑犯持「行街紙」，女事主丈夫持香港身分證。<br />\nSource:星島"},{"pid":"3db28e26771ba7905dd2141067ca1f7ab93e0b82","tid":1970152,"uid":34551,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T02:46:08.000Z","msg":"我睇唔透發生咩事"},{"pid":"c6a5b7a6ca44644d3451e143d3d62e68f3ee6be2","tid":1970152,"uid":4574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T02:46:10.000Z","msg":"少女唔鋤"},{"pid":"0f330b6fc1c69dd6e7f68de8411344ca38b63c01","tid":1970152,"uid":216127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T02:46:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7ca102fb4d2b5f827d9166647e6e4ba3978437f7","tid":1970152,"uid":30067,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T02:48:43.000Z","msg":"27印男 同 43港婦 vs 23印色狼"},{"pid":"067c22fc1bec83b50859becd33e1bb48c30f39b7","tid":1970152,"uid":89869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7ca102fb4d2b5f827d9166647e6e4ba3978437f7","tid":1970152,"uid":30067,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T02:48:43.000Z","msg":"27印男 同 43港婦 vs 23印色狼"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T02:49:38.000Z","msg":"簡單易明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"931429f1dadcf57f85d5f012c5aab633c5a991b7","tid":1970152,"uid":199670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T02:49:39.000Z","msg":"43本地 食27歲印度腸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ador